targets.rawSql:
SELECT
  year as "Time",
  name,
  minute as "exercise"
FROM
  exercise
WHERE year in ($year) AND name in ($exercise_sort)
order by year;

SELECT
  year as "Time",
  name,
  minute as "home_exercise"
FROM
  home_exercise
WHERE year in ($year) AND name in ($exercise_sort)
order by year;
select name, ((sum(minute)/60)/100)*100 as 분 from home_exercise where name in ('Elbow plank') group by name, minute
select name, sum(minute)/60 as 초 from home_exercise where name in ('Plank twist') group by name, minute
select $__time(year), name, minute/ 60  as " "  from home_exercise;
select name, sum(minute)/60 as 초 from home_exercise where name in ('Elbow plank') group by name, minute
select name, sum(minute)/60 as 초 from home_exercise where name in ('Plank twist') group by name, minute
select $__time(year), name, minute/ 60  as " "  from home_exercise;
select $__time(year), name, count_m  as " "  from home_exercise;
select $__time(year), name, count_m  as " "  from home_exercise;

list.definition:
select to_char(exercise.year, 'yyyy-mm-dd') as year from  exercise 
union all
select to_char(home_exercise.year, 'yyyy-mm-dd')as year from  home_exercise
order by year DESC
;
